        Oh — OH.

        Scout bounces — they understand what this means: the answer we've been waiting for, *THE* answer.

        I say to Buddy, "This is it — this is the Oracle episode."

        Buddy confirms, "Season four, episode twelve — when Mav finally reaches the Oracle of Veris after his whole journey. The moment of truth!"

